WEBVTT

00:02:28.583 --> 00:02:30.518
the former president of Venezuela.

00:02:30.542 --> 00:02:31.559
(Laughter)

00:02:31.583 --> 00:02:34.125
(Speaks Spanish)

00:02:39.833 --> 00:02:42.226
All of this happened
after the newspaper was bought

00:02:42.250 --> 00:02:43.809
by an unknown company,

00:02:43.833 --> 00:02:45.226
and some of us suspect

00:02:45.250 --> 00:02:48.583
that it was the Venezuelan government
who was behind that deal.

00:02:48.958 --> 00:02:52.750
(Speaks Spanish)

00:02:59.833 --> 00:03:02.559
My work as a cartoonist
became more and more of a nuisance